\<build\>
 \<plugins\>

 \<\!\-\- Plugin to compile the g4 files ahead of the java files
 See https\://github\.com/antlr/antlr4/blob/master/antlr4\-maven\-plugin/src/site/apt/exa mples/simple\.apt\.vm
 Except that the grammar does not need to contain the package declaration as stated in the documentation \(I do not know why\)
 To use this plugin\, type\:
 mvn antlr4\:antlr4

In any case\, Maven will invoke this plugin before the Java source
is compiled
 \-\-\>
 \<plugin\>
 \<groupId\>org\.antlr\</groupId\>
 \<artifactId\>antlr4\-maven\-plugin\</artifactId\>
 \<version\>4\.7\</version\>
 \<executions\>
 \<execution\>
 \<goals\>


\<goal\>antlr4\</goal\>

\</goals\>

\</execution\>

\</executions\>

\</plugin\>



\</plugins\>
